2. Package-free state machine smoke test

Temporary project:
- `/tmp/lulupet-p5-smoke/P5Smoke.csproj`
- References `src/LuluPet.Core/LuluPet.Core.csproj`
- Uses no NuGet test packages.

Command:

dotnet restore /tmp/lulupet-p5-smoke/P5Smoke.csproj \
  --configfile /tmp/lulupet-offline-nuget.config

dotnet run --project /tmp/lulupet-p5-smoke/P5Smoke.csproj --no-restore

Result:
- P5 smoke test passed.

Smoke test coverage:
- Idle -> Walk when walk probability succeeds.
- Walk -> Idle after fixed walk duration.
- Long Idle -> Sleep when sleep probability succeeds.
- Sleep -> Idle after fixed sleep duration.
- Walk does not reset cumulative awake time; Sleep can still occur after walking.
- StateChanged transition order for Idle -> Walk -> Idle.

